### Beneficiaries (favorites) — list, create-after-transfer rule, delete.
### Self-contained: run top to bottom (includes the prerequisite transfer).

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("token", response.body.accessToken);
%}

### Source account
GET {{baseUrl}}/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

> {%
    client.global.set("accountId", response.body[0].id);
%}

### List favorites — "Budi" is seeded
GET {{baseUrl}}/beneficiaries
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Prerequisite: transfer to the destination we want to save (README §5.5 rule)
POST {{baseUrl}}/transfers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceAccountId": "{{accountId}}",
  "destBankCode": "MANDIRI",
  "destAccountNumber": "9988776655",
  "destAccountName": "SITI AMINAH",
  "amount": 50000,
  "method": "BI_FAST",
  "note": "first transfer before saving favorite",
  "pin": "123456"
}

### Save it as a favorite → 201 (409 BENEFICIARY_EXISTS on a second run)
POST {{baseUrl}}/beneficiaries
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "alias": "Siti",
  "bankCode": "MANDIRI",
  "accountNumber": "9988776655",
  "accountName": "SITI AMINAH"
}

> {%
    if (response.status === 201) {
        client.global.set("beneficiaryId", response.body.id);
    }
%}

### Never-transferred destination → 400 NO_PRIOR_TRANSFER
POST {{baseUrl}}/beneficiaries
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "alias": "Unknown",
  "bankCode": "BNI",
  "accountNumber": "0000000001",
  "accountName": "UNKNOWN PERSON"
}

### Delete the favorite created above → 204
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/beneficiaries/{{beneficiaryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete an unknown favorite → 404
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/beneficiaries/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
